---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section class="bg-white py-8 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div
          class="flex justify-center pb-4  items-center flex-col sm:flex-row space-y-3 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4"
        >
        <a
          href="#analyze"
          class="relative overflow-hidden bg-white text-[#0c285e] border border-[#0c285e] hover:bg-[#0c285e] hover:text-white hover:border-white hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,255,255,0.8)] transition-all duration-300 font-medium sm:font-semibold px-8 sm:px-8 py-3 sm:py-6 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl text-center text-sm sm:text-base before:absolute before:inset-0 before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-transparent before:via-white before:to-transparent before:opacity-0 hover:before:opacity-20 before:transition-opacity before:duration-500"
        >
        Be first with us as a Development Partner
        </a>
      </div>
      <!-- develoment parnet -->
      <div id="analyze" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto my-12">
        <div class="relative mb-12 overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0c285e]/90 to-[#0c285e]/70 z-10"></div>
          <Image src="/images/development-partnership.jpg" width={1200} height={400} alt="Development Partnership" class="w-full h-64 md:h-80 object-cover" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 z-20 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white p-6 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold mb-4 animate-fade-in">
              What's a Development Partnership?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl">Join an exclusive program for 8 select partners to co-develop AI solutions tailored to your business</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-8 animate-slide-up text-lg md:text-xl" style="--animation-delay: 0.1s;">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 text-[#0c285e]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
            <p>Automation and AI analytics are transforming the efficiency and competitiveness of the PL and GL insurance sectors. That's why we're launching an exclusive program for 8 select partners to co-develop AI solutions tailored to your business.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 text-[#0c285e]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
            </svg>
            <p>You understand the unique needs of your Brokerage, Carrier, or Management business—and we specialize in engineering AI and automation solutions that help grow your book of business, cut down on claims and liability, and drive down operating costs.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 text-[#0c285e]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
            <p>You don't want to be married to a never-ending tech bill. We don't want to guess what solutions your business needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-16">
          <div class="animate-slide-up" style="--animation-delay: 0.3s;">
            <div class="relative mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
              <Image src="/images/handshake.jpg" width={600} height={400} alt="Partnership Agreement" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-[#0c285e] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-[#0c285e]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2" />
              </svg>
              Here's the offer:
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 pl-2 text-lg md:text-xl">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4 hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 mt-0 flex-shrink-0 text-green-600 animate-pulse" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                We pay 90% of the development cost
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4 hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 mt-0 flex-shrink-0 text-green-600 animate-pulse" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                You pay 10% of the development cost
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4 hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 mt-0 flex-shrink-0 text-green-600 animate-pulse" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                We guarantee the delivery date of your custom solution
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4 hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 mt-0 flex-shrink-0 text-green-600 animate-pulse" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                You specify what you want our engineers to build
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="animate-slide-up" style="--animation-delay: 0.5s;">
            <div class="relative mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
              <Image src="/images/tech-solution.jpg" width={600} height={400} alt="Custom Solutions" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 text-lg md:text-xl">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 border border-blue-100 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300 bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-blue-50">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 text-[#0c285e]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p>You pay a fixed fee between $5,000 and $30,000 per month, depending on complexity, for a maximum of 4 months.</p>
                  <p class="mt-2">We commit to commissioning your new solution within 3 to 4 months for that fixed fee.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 text-[#0c285e]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                </svg>
                <p>You commit to a clear specification and timely testing—because success depends on both of us.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 text-center animate-slide-up" style="--animation-delay: 0.7s;">
          <div class="inline-block p-8 border-t border-[#0c285e]/20">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-8 mb-8">
              <div class="relative w-64 h-64 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-[#0c285e]/20">
                <Image src="/images/grow.jpg" width={300} height={300} alt="Win-Win Partnership" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#0c285e] font-medium flex items-center justify-center gap-3 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 mb-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-green-600 animate-bounce" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
                  </svg>
                  You win.
                </p>
                <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#0c285e] font-medium flex items-center justify-center gap-3 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 mb-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-green-600 animate-bounce" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
                  </svg>
                  We win.
                </p>
                <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#0c285e] font-medium flex items-center justify-center gap-3 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 mb-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-green-600 animate-bounce" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
                  </svg>
                  Our customers win.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-[#0c285e] font-semibold">That's the Alliance in Senior Care Alliance</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Logo static display -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="partners-grid flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-10 lg:gap-16">
          <div class="w-40 lg:w-48 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
            <Image src="/images/Nationwide.svg" width={300} height={400} alt="Nationwide Insurance" class="h-16 lg:h-20 object-contain" />
          </div>
          <div class="w-40 lg:w-48 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
            <Image src="/images/chubb-logo.svg" width={300} height={300} alt="Chubb Insurance" class="h-16 lg:h-20 object-contain" />
          </div>
          <div class="w-40 lg:w-48 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
            <Image src="/images/liberty-mutual.svg" width={300} height={300} alt="Liberty Express Insurance" class="h-16 lg:h-20 object-contain" />
          </div>
          <div class="w-40 lg:w-48 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
            <Image src="/images/AIG.svg" width={300} height={300} alt="AIG Insurance" class="h-16 lg:h-20 object-contain" />
          </div>
          <div class="w-40 lg:w-48 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
            <Image src="/images/medpro-logo.svg" width={300} height={300} alt="MedPro Insurance" class="h-16 lg:h-20 object-contain" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* For smooth hover effects */
  .partners-grid > div {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .partners-grid > div:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  /* Animations */
  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-in-out forwards;
  }

  .animate-slide-up {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: slideUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: var(--animation-delay, 0s);
  }

  .animate-pulse {
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  .animate-bounce {
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
    animation-delay: var(--animation-delay, 0s);
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  @keyframes slideUp {
    from { 
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to { 
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.6; }
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
  }
</style> 